title: Biden HOT MIC Has White House SPINNING
author: G. Mcconway
excerpt: What the heck is he talking about?
summary:
Oh, Joe, what lies are you telling now? Biden was caught on a hot mic during his visit to El Paso this weekend.
During a photo op at the Salvation Army, Joe Biden told an official that he spent time with the Secret Service in Poland and Ukraine. Only nobody knows what the hell he is talking about. What the…
Joe Biden was shaking hands with one of the officials when a microphone picked up some chit-chat between the official and Joe Biden.
Not all of what they were saying was audible, but you could hear Biden, at one point, state, 'I spent some time with the Secret Service in Poland and in Ukraine.

title: US Dem. calls Biden 'war criminal' over Ukraine, Yemen, Iraq, Syria
author: Al Mayadeen English

summary:
By
Al Mayadeen English

Source: Agencies
 Today 10:27

 The candidate for Kentucky congressional seat says all US presidents since 1945 are war criminals.


US President Joe Biden



A US candidate for Kentucky's governor seat accused US President Joe Biden of war crimes in Ukraine, Yemen, Syria, and Iraq, as well as other countries, and called for his impeachment.
Geoffrey Young also called out the sitting US President for his ongoing "illegal proxy war against Russia in Ukraine," adding that all American presidents since 1945 are war criminals.

title: A loving dad and his injured son pay war's costs in Ukraine
author: Hanna Arhirova
excerpt: In a Ukrainian hospital ward for wounded soldiers, where daylight barely penetrates, a father talks to his injured son for hours. Serhii Shumei, 64, never scolded Vitalii for choosing to go to war.
summary: CHERNIHIV, Ukraine — In a Ukrainian hospital ward for wounded soldiers, where daylight barely penetrates, a father talks to his injured son for hours. Serhii Shumei, 64, never scolded Vitalii for choosing to go to war. Even now, despite the damage done to his son's brain by an exploding artillery shell, Serhii feels pride, not pity."I've been constantly with him in the last five months, beside him, beside him, beside him," said Serhii, a retired soldier himself. "I'm not going anywhere. … except for a smoke.
authors: Andrew Harnik,Associated Press,Carolyn Kaster,Efrem Lukatsky,Hanna Arhirova,Jacquelyn Martin,Patrick Semansky

title: Comer: Hunter's Driver's License Displays Joe Biden's Delaware Address
author: Wendell Husebø
excerpt: Rep. James Comer confirmed the address on Hunter's driver's license is the same as Joe Biden's Delaware residence.
summary:
Rep. James Comer (R-KY), the chair of the House Oversight Committee, confirmed that the address on Hunter's driver's license is the same as Joe Biden's Delaware residence.
Comer's report verifies that Hunter had access to Joe Biden's home where a trove of classified documents was stashed.


'Documents on file with the Committee reveal the same address appeared on Hunter Biden's driver's license as recently as 2018,' Comer notifed the White House. 'The Committee is concerned President Biden stored classified documents at the same location his son resided while engaging in international business deals with adversaries of the United States.

title: Report: Doc Shows Hunter Owned Joe Biden's Delaware House in 2018
author: Wendell Husebø
excerpt: Hunter Biden owned Joe Biden's Delaware house in 2018, where the elder Biden has now been discovered to have stashed classified documents.
summary:
Hunter Biden owned President Joe Biden's Delaware house in 2018, where the elder Biden has now been discovered to have stashed classified documents, according to a document unearthed by New York Post's Miranda Devine on Thursday.
On a document titled, 'background screening request,' it appears Hunter checked a box to indicate he owned Joe Biden's home located in Wilmington, Delaware. The document is signed July, 2018.

In 2018 Hunter Biden claimed he owned the house where Joe Biden kept classified documents alongside his Corvette in the garage Via @jj_talking pic.

title: Dutch PM signals 'intention' to send Patriots to Ukraine
author: France 24
excerpt: Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte signaled his "intention" Tuesday during a meeting with President Joe Biden to follow Germany in its delivery of US-made Patriot air-defense missiles to Ukraine.
summary:
US President Joe Biden meets with Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte in the Oval Office of the White House

Washington (AFP) – Dutch Prime Minister Mark Rutte signaled his "intention" Tuesday during a meeting with President Joe Biden to follow Germany in its delivery of US-made Patriot air-defense missiles to Ukraine.

Advertising Read more

"We have the intention to join what you're doing with Germany on the Patriots project, the air-defense system. I think that is important and we joined that," Rutte told Biden in the White House, adding that he had "discussed it also this morning" with German Chancellor Olaf Scholz.
